OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776272750
OL,3,CCampaigners disagree on
OL,4,C'environmentally responsible' goldmine
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FA public inquiry into plans to build a
OL,8,Fgoldmine near Greencastle in Co Tyrone
OL,9,Fhas resumed in Omagh after collapsing
OL,10,Flast year because of a blunder by the
OL,11,FDepartment for Infrastructure.
OL,13,FCanadian Company Dalradian claimed the
OL,14,Fgoldmine could be worth billions to
OL,15,Fthe economy in Northern Ireland, and
OL,16,Ftheir plans, originally submitted over
OL,17,Feight years ago, are "environmentally
OL,18,Fresponsible".
OL,20,FCampaigners opposed to the project,
OL,21,Fhowever, disagree.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
