OL,3,CCampaigners disagree on
OL,4,C'environmentally responsible' goldmine
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,F"We are concerned about the water, the
OL,8,Fair, the land and the health, things
OL,9,Fthat are basic to our survival, and
OL,10,Fthat's what's important," Fidelma
OL,11,FO'Kane of Save Our Sperrins Group said.
OL,13,F"It's not about money for people in
OL,14,FAmerica or Canada, or profits for
OL,15,Fbusinesses. This is part of us.
OL,17,F"We live in the Sperrins, we love the
OL,18,FSperrins, and we want it to be safe
OL,19,Ffor our grandchildren and future
OL,20,Fgenerations to live there."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
