OL,3,CCampaigners disagree on
OL,4,C'environmentally responsible' goldmine
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FThe inquiry by the Planning Appeals
OL,8,FCommission is expected to last up to
OL,9,F10 weeks.
OL,11,FOriginally the public inquiry
OL,12,Fcollapsed in January 2025 after two
OL,13,Fdays of evidence when the Department
OL,14,Ffor Infrastructure failed to follow
OL,15,Fits own process by not notifying the
OL,16,FIrish Government about the planning
OL,17,Fapplication and the public inquiry.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
